    • ScoreSamplingOptions

      public ScoreSamplingOptions(int numThreads, Integer minObjectId, Integer maxObjectId, int minNumTerms, int maxNumTerms, int seed, int numIterations)
      Construct with specific values for the options.
      Parameters:
      numThreads - Number of threads to use.
      minObjectId - Smallest "world object" Id to use or null for no lower bound.
      maxObjectId - Largest "world object" Id to use or null for no upper bound.
      minNumTerms - Smallest number of terms to compute precomputation for.
      maxNumTerms - Largest number of terms to compute precomputation for.
      numIterations - The number of iterations to run for.
      seed - The seed to use for the computation.
